{"tid":1118311,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"送面膜粉 未開封未過期","createTime":"2019-04-21T10:19:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-21T19:05:45.000Z","uid":190135,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"82e67b83e62150a94fa712337116b16df6eba3be","tid":1118311,"uid":190135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T10:19:56.000Z","msg":"樓主我3月份買左幾包草藥面膜粉 <br />\n保質期三年 所以有排都未到期嘅<br />\n用完塊面就勁敏感 又冇得退貨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應該話有得退貨 但又唔會退錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咪即係退比佢再賣過 等於一件貨佢賺兩次錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係咁想益商家 所以益下連登巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ts6Pw1V.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTs6Pw1V.png&h=2c8616fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我買左5包 一包開左 所以仲有4包 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n功效成份圖入面有寫<br />\n唔係賣廣告 詳細資料就自己上網睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開出黎好大陣草藥味 唔中意就唔好要喇 唔想浪費<br />\n另外容易敏感嘅人自己衡量風險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果想要可以留tg <br />\n順豐到付"},{"pid":"5ab711bb9145c241650e77163ceaa08a20fabdfd","tid":1118311,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T10:47:33.000Z","msg":"絲打有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"175f5995c6e84430c68d553374ba808754caa97c","tid":1118311,"uid":140599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T11:07:21.000Z","msg":"小弟有意 <a href=\"https://t.me/wemoxchich\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fwemoxchich&d=CcUT5H46krin9iWjsTG5RD2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=65e36db3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/wemoxchich</a>"},{"pid":"fbf855c59faba7e13dbb0dbefb14de01ef73cf3a","tid":1118311,"uid":70417,"like":0,"dislike